hypothetical spherical crystal

00:27:41.050 --> 00:27:44.560
field, where all the d
orbitals have the same energy.

00:27:44.560 --> 00:27:46.330
And if you put your
electrons in here,

00:27:46.330 --> 00:27:50.590
where they'd all have the same
energy, to the diff energy

00:27:50.590 --> 00:27:53.290
