energies-- when you're placing

00:27:53.290 --> 00:27:56.830
the electrons in lower energy
orbitals or higher energy

00:27:56.830 --> 00:27:57.550
orbitals.

00:27:57.550 --> 00:28:00.750
So you're thinking about
how much more stabilized

00:28:00.750 --> 00:28:04.370
is the system if all of the
electrons are down here.

00:28:04.370 --> 00:28:06.010
That's going to be
stabilized compared

00:28:06.010 --> 00:28:07.330
