00:28:34.150 --> 00:28:37.060
Three go down in energy,
so that's minus 2.

00:28:37.060 --> 00:28:39.580
Two go up in energy,
again, plus 3.

00:28:39.580 --> 00:28:42.880
And then we have two
electrons up here.

00:28:42.880 --> 00:28:47.890
