00:39:01.230 --> 00:39:02.790
to absorb a photon or not.

00:39:02.790 --> 00:39:06.600
And it will if the
energy of that photon

00:39:06.600 --> 00:39:09.850
is equal to the difference
in that energy level.

00:39:09.850 --> 00:39:11.470
So we talked about this before.

00:39:11.470 --> 00:39:14.700
Exam one, exam two,
