00:39:14.700 --> 00:39:17.820
And so, we saw this
equation a lot.

00:39:17.820 --> 00:39:20.760
That the energy equals Planck's
constant, times the frequency

00:39:20.760 --> 00:39:21.780
of the light.

00:39:21.780 --> 00:39:24.750
And now we can take that
same gorgeous equation

00:39:24.750 --> 00:39:26.610
and add a little thing to it.

00:39:26.610 --> 00:39:28.320
So we can add that
