00:39:28.320 --> 00:39:32.130
going to be equal to the
octahedral crystal field

00:39:32.130 --> 00:39:34.240
splitting energy.

00:39:34.240 --> 00:39:37.380
And so, a substance, one
of these transition metal

00:39:37.380 --> 00:39:41.010
complexes, will absorb
a photon of light

00:39:41.010 --> 00:39:44.550
if the energy of that photon
is equal to this splitting

00:39:44.550 --> 00:39:45.510
difference.

00:39:45.510 --> 00:39:49.800
And if it is, it can promote
an electron between a lower

00:39:49.800 --> 00:39:51.630
and a higher state.

